      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried all that. health checks are passing, cpu/mem is low, and the code is just a simple express app, nothing crazy. the timeout happens exactly at 30s every time which feels like a config thing. i dont have much time before this deploy... can u just give me the specific config change or command to fix the timeout so i can get this ticket closed and move on? i just need it to work now.",
